{"tid":382888,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［香港無毒戲］有毒嘅係毒品，定係我哋嘅說話？","createTime":"2017-09-01T05:10:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T09:52:10.000Z","uid":138478,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e9896d75ed65cdfebb68a8dd3731729db5ad2695","tid":382888,"uid":138478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T05:10:22.000Z","msg":"《香港無毒戲》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5puSWxtx7oQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5puSWxtx7oQ&d=Iyc%2FzmFkNyrh6TxhnKm032Mi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=a5758701\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5puSWxtx7oQ</a><br />\n<br />\n各位巴打絲打，今日小弟Po文宣傳一下我哋團隊最近製作嘅禁毒短片，希望你願意花1分鐘時間觀賞，然後投下你寶貴嘅一票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （當然如果覺得太差唔想就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n我哋段片希望令大家反思禁毒嘅方法唔單止在於限制毒品嘅流出，更加在於我哋嘅一言一語。因為比起毒品，更多時候令人沉淪嘅，係我哋一句無心但又令人痛心嘅說話，而呢啲說話，有時候足以令一個人以毒品逃避所有討厭嘅事物。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果願意支持小弟團隊嘅製作，希望留下一個讚好投票，你嘅支持會促進我哋創作嘅動力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果有咩意見都歡迎提出比我地改善。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5969889b457fa86e7cd253b5312ffb43ca15a730","tid":382888,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T05:23:19.000Z","msg":"首先，你個標題講緊乜"},{"pid":"7fa4d2522e7176721c6389cfa2f6396583307841","tid":382888,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T05:53:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首先，你個標題講緊乜</blockquote><br />\n邊句唔明？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3afb74f1fb8815f69ea7028083b0696415bd9253","tid":382888,"uid":7452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T06:09:07.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"08a03d6a2e2d6ca73a1de091930d8de764ed7547","tid":382888,"uid":44461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T06:19:05.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得有啲失焦，明明個比賽應該係講禁毒，但你地又聚焦左落啲人苛刻嘅說話到，其實唔理你地點自圓其說都好，我都想講呢條片同禁毒都無咩關係，無論係「禁」又好，「毒」又好都無咩關係"},{"pid":"98bce553100ffc0ab49efc8e0e5a81566e972638","tid":382888,"uid":138478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:45:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1999</blockquote><br />\nsor for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad84f6ae7e25b9de4e878216adc65c6826a304bb","tid":382888,"uid":138478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T09:52:10.000Z","msg":"推"}]}